# Customer Segmentation Project

## Objective
Segment customers based on behavior and demographics.

## Key Features
- Perform clustering using Python (scikit-learn) or Power BI
- Analyze purchase patterns and customer preferences
- Visualize customer segments and key characteristics

## Tools
- Python
- Scikit-learn
- Pandas
- Matplotlib
- Power BI

## Workflow
1. Data Collection
2. Data Cleaning
3. Feature Selection
4. Customer Clustering
5. Segment Analysis
6. Visualization
7. Business Insights

## Expected Outcome
Gain experience in:
- Customer Analytics
- Customer Segmentation
- Data Visualization
- Business Intelligence
- Targeted Marketing Insights

## Future Improvements
- Predict customer lifetime value
- Recommendation systems
- Advanced clustering techniques
